Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.20,0:02:56.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\an9\fs40}註：想登塔嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.73,0:13:53.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fn方正喵呜_GBK\fs70\c&H000000&\bord0\frz25.1\pos(755.77,232.8)}想繼續登塔嗎
